      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-02-16T18:34:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t know how progress sink will react if we continue to report errors after it is terminated. How about I move up the check so that progress gRPC will be consistent with results.json and streamed_results.jsonl?",
