      "side": 1,
      "message": "PS6 still makes inconsistency between 1 vs. 2/3.\n\nI think we should align to what we have today within Tast. If F20 spec doesn\u0027t want us to report results after termination, tast_rtd can filter results. But anyway, I\u0027m optimistic that TLW should allow results after termination since termination support is optional IIUC.",
